    <p>This scheme helps all who are charged with cap­i­tal of­fences such as mur­der and kid­nap­ping, re­gard­less of na­tion­al­ity.</p>
    <p>Free legal coun­sel is as­signed to peo­ple fac­ing cap­i­tal charges, and there is no el­i­gi­bil­ity cri­te­ria for this scheme.</p>
    <p>Some of the or­gan­i­sa­tions that run legal clin­ics in­clude: • Sin­ga­pore Man­age­ment Univer­sity’s Pro Bono Cen­tre</p>
    <p>• Mi­grant Work­ers’ Cen­tre</p>
    <p>• Com­mu­nity Jus­tice Cen­tre</p>


